            . I am an officer. I went to the prisoner's room, and found this property; he said the<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="182705310116"></xptr>leather was his own, and that his wife had brought the cap home.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I did a little work on my own account. I only earned 10s. a week with him. I have had the leather three years, and can produce a pair of my children's boots made from the leather.</p>
               <p>B. W. VALENTINE. He said he had bought the leather some time ago.</p>
               <p>ROBERT BURROWS. Our private mark is on it.</p>
               <p>GUILTY. Aged 36.</p>
